CREATE TABLE `doc-ai-studio.qsight_test.EncounterProduct`
(
  EncounterProductId STRING NOT NULL,
  EncounterId STRING NOT NULL,
  ProductVariantId STRING NOT NULL,
  InventoryTransactionTypeId STRING NOT NULL,
  Quantity INT64,
  Deleted BOOL NOT NULL,
  Consigned BOOL NOT NULL,
  ContrastId STRING,
  Notes STRING(255),
  BillingExportId STRING,
  DateCreated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  DateLastModified TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
PARTITION BY DATE(DateCreated);
